pr_title: Bump bounds to build on latest lts-20

pr_body:
- separates out the part of the runtime depended on by domains
- removes functions for commands
- removes `NoResponse`
-  removes the need for different functions depending on whether a command has an expected response or not. Instead, 2 functions are provided to send commands, returning a promise or the result (after waiting)
- updates examples and tests
